channel.title: Server won't go online
channel.description:
I don't understand why it won't work.. I have done all the portforwarding necessary to get it done. Tell me if I am wrong on this:
I portforwarded, and have IpDuc (did all the work with that, clicked the checkbox) as well as changed my TC/IP settings for it to work. I am doing it for a friend, I had a server 2 years ago and I am wondering what I am not doing. Client side we did the GUI.Java changed the 127.0 etc. Is there anything I have to do server side. I am using Combattscape as a source, for further information here is the download link I have created to share the info through my friend and it's the same .RAR file as the one I downloaded at the beginning.
[url=http://www.mediafire.com/?pgg5v5zcuc23g8d]http://www.mediafire.com/?pgg5v5zcuc23g8d[/url]
